  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall aim of this study is to develop and test a psychodynamic Internet-delivered
      psychological treatment for patients with major depression and/or anxiety disorders and
      compare its efficacy to an active control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
